{
    "c1": {
        "title": "1. Smart Queue",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nUniversal entry point for the MCR Engine. Handles initial load distribution.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Accepts JSON payload via FastAPI\n> 2) Normalizes request headers\n> 3) Generates SHA-256 state hash\n> 4) Subscribes duplicate hits to existing thread",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-400 border-b border-blue-900 pb-2\">1. SMART QUEUE INTERNALS</h2>\n            <div class=\"flex gap-8 items-center w-full max-w-4xl justify-center relative\">\n                <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-6 rounded shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center w-48 z-10\">\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-file-code text-4xl text-slate-500 mb-4\"></i>\n                    <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-slate-300\">Raw MCP JSON</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"h-1 w-24 bg-blue-900/50 flex-shrink-0 animate-pulse relative\">\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute right-0 -top-1.5 text-blue-500\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/50 p-6 rounded shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(59,130,246,0.2)] flex flex-col items-center w-48 z-10 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI0MCI+PGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMjAiIGN5PSIyMCIgcj0iMSIgZmlsbD0iIzFZTjI5M0IiLz48L3N2Zz4=')] opacity-20\"></div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-filter text-4xl text-blue-400 mb-4\"></i>\n                    <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-blue-300 font-bold mb-2\">DEDUPLICATOR</span>\n                    <span class=\"font-mono text-[8px] bg-black/50 p-1 px-2 rounded text-blue-200\">SHA-256 Hash Check</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"h-1 w-24 bg-blue-900/50 flex-shrink-0 animate-pulse relative\">\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute right-0 -top-1.5 text-blue-500\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-6 rounded shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center w-48 z-10\">\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-layer-group text-4xl text-slate-500 mb-4\"></i>\n                    <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-slate-300\">Active Task ID</span>\n                    <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-emerald-500 mt-2\">req_mcr_99...</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center mt-8\">The Queue prevents system flooding. If a second user requests the exact same schema mutation while one is currently executing, it simply subscribes the second user to the outcome of the first task rather than re-spinning the entire architecture.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c2": {
        "title": "2. Complexity Appraiser",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nDetermines exact computational tier before consuming cluster resources.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Rule-based matching heuristics\n> 2) LIGHT TIER: Cached / Known path\n> 3) MEDIUM TIER: Requires mapping\n> 4) HEAVY TIER: Forces generative pipeline",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-amber-500 border-b border-amber-900 pb-2\">2. COMPLEXITY APPRAISER</h2>\n            <div class=\"flex gap-12 w-full max-w-5xl justify-center items-start\">\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-emerald-900/20 border border-emerald-500/50 p-6 rounded shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(16,185,129,0.1)] w-56 text-center\">\n                        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-feather text-4xl text-emerald-400 mb-4 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)]\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-emerald-400 tracking-widest\">LIGHT TIER</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[9px] text-emerald-200/70 mt-2 font-mono leading-relaxed\">Known schemas, repetitive tasks, static data syncs.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long text-slate-600\"></i>\n                    <div class=\"text-[9px] font-mono bg-[#020510] border border-slate-700 p-2 rounded text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap\">Routes to Cache (Hit)</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mt-8\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/50 p-6 rounded shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(59,130,246,0.1)] w-56 text-center scale-110 relative\">\n                        <div class=\"absolute -inset-1 bg-blue-500/20 blur-xl z-0 rounded-full\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n                            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-weight-hanging text-4xl text-blue-400 mb-4 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(59,130,246,0.5)]\"></i>\n                            <h3 class=\"font-bold text-blue-400 tracking-widest\">MEDIUM TIER</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-[9px] text-blue-200/70 mt-2 font-mono leading-relaxed\">Unknown data schemas, standard transformations.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long text-blue-500 animate-pulse text-xl\"></i>\n                    <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono bg-[#06162a] border border-blue-800 p-2 rounded text-blue-300 font-bold whitespace-nowrap shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.2)]\">Routes to Assembly</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-rose-900/20 border border-rose-500/50 p-6 rounded shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(244,63,94,0.1)] w-56 text-center\">\n                        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-dumbbell text-4xl text-rose-400 mb-4 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(244,63,94,0.5)]\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-rose-400 tracking-widest\">HEAVY TIER</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-[9px] text-rose-200/70 mt-2 font-mono leading-relaxed\">Complex logic synthesis, destructive database operations.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long text-slate-600\"></i>\n                    <div class=\"text-[9px] font-mono bg-[#020510] border border-slate-700 p-2 rounded text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap\">Routes to Assembly (w/ HITL)</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center mt-12 leading-loose\">The Appraiser instantly categorizes the structural weight of the intent payload to prevent trivial requests from consuming expensive generative AI compute time.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c3": {
        "title": "3/4. Planner & Registry",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nDeconstructs objectives and checks historical cache for existing solutions.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Planner agent builds DAG workflow\n> 2) Curator attempts Vector Query on DB\n> 3) Hit: Bypass to Virtualization\n> 4) Miss: Route to Assembly",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-indigo-400 border-b border-indigo-900 pb-2\">3/4. PLANNER & REGISTRY</h2>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-12 w-full\">\n                <!-- Planner -->\n                <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-80\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\">\n                        <div class=\"bg-indigo-900/50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-indigo-500\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-diagram-project text-2xl text-indigo-400\"></i></div>\n                        <div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white\">PLANNER AGENT</h3><p class=\"text-[10px] uppercase font-mono tracking-widest text-indigo-500\">DAG Generator</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n                        <div class=\"bg-black/50 p-2 rounded border border-slate-800 flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-mono\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-check text-indigo-500\"></i> Parse JSON Intent</div>\n                        <div class=\"bg-black/50 p-2 rounded border border-slate-800 flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-mono\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-check text-indigo-500\"></i> Construct Dependency Graph</div>\n                        <div class=\"bg-indigo-900/20 p-2 rounded border border-indigo-900/50 flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] text-indigo-300 font-mono font-bold animate-pulse\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-indigo-400\"></i> Interrogate Registry</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- Connecting lines -->\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center\">\n                    <div class=\"h-1 w-24 bg-indigo-900/50\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-indigo-500 bg-[#060b1a] px-2 -mt-2.5 outline outline-4 outline-[#060b1a]\">COSINE SIMILARITY</div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- Registry -->\n                <div class=\"bg-[#020510] border border-blue-900/50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(59,130,246,0.15)] w-80 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI0MCI+PGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMjAiIGN5PSIyMCIgcj0iMSIgZmlsbD0iIzFZTjI5M0IiLz48L3N2Zz4=')] opacity-10\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\">\n                            <div class=\"bg-blue-900/50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-blue-500\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-database text-2xl text-blue-400\"></i></div>\n                            <div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white\">VERIFIED REGISTRY</h3><p class=\"text-[10px] uppercase font-mono tracking-widest text-blue-500\">Vector Cache</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                            <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border-l-2 border-emerald-500 p-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400\">[x] Routine: SAP_Invoice_Sync</div>\n                            <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border-l-2 border-emerald-500 p-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400\">[x] Routine: Stripe_Webhook_ETL</div>\n                            <div class=\"bg-slate-900 border-l-2 border-slate-700 p-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500 line-through\">[ ] Routine: MSSQL_Schema_Spider</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center mt-4\">The Planner constructs a Directed Acyclic Graph (DAG) for the goal. It then instantly queries the Registry (a massive vector database of previously solved problems) looking for a Cache Hit to avoid regenerating logic.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c5": {
        "title": "5. AssemblyEngine",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nAutonomous generation of executable Python logic.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Finder Agent pulls destination schemas\n> 2) Codegen writes AST Python logic\n> 3) Emits simulated Unit Tests",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-amber-500 border-b border-amber-900 pb-2\">5. ASSEMBLY ENGINE & CODEGEN</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full max-w-5xl mt-8\">\n                <!-- Finder Agent -->\n                <div class=\"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700 p-6 rounded flex flex-col items-center relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 bg-blue-900/80 border border-blue-500 text-blue-300 text-[8px] px-2 py-1 rounded-br-lg z-20\">T1: GATHER</div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-3xl text-slate-500 group-hover:text-blue-400 mb-3 transition-colors text-shadow\"></i>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-300 text-xs mb-2\">FINDER AGENT</h3>\n                    <ul class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-mono list-disc pl-4 space-y-1\">\n                        <li>Fetch API Spec</li>\n                        <li>Map Data Types</li>\n                        <li>Find Authorization tokens</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Codegen Agent -->\n                <div class=\"bg-amber-900/20 border border-amber-700/50 p-6 rounded flex flex-col items-center relative shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.1)]\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 bg-amber-900/80 border border-amber-500 text-amber-300 text-[8px] px-2 py-1 rounded-br-lg z-20\">T2: SYNTHESIZE</div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-laptop-code text-4xl text-amber-400 mb-3 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(245,158,11,0.5)]\"></i>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-amber-400 text-xs mb-2\">CODEGEN AGENT</h3>\n                    <div class=\"bg-black/60 border border-amber-900/50 w-full p-2 rounded text-[8px] font-mono text-amber-200/70 h-16 overflow-hidden relative\">\n                        def execute_mutation(payload):<br>\n                        &nbsp;&nbsp;mapped_data = transform(payload)<br>\n                        &nbsp;&nbsp;return api.post(\"/v1/mutate\", data=mapped_data)\n                        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-black\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Abstract Modeler -->\n                <div class=\"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700 p-6 rounded flex flex-col items-center relative group hover:border-emerald-500 transition-colors\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-3 -left-3 bg-emerald-900/80 border border-emerald-500 text-emerald-300 text-[8px] px-2 py-1 rounded-br-lg z-20\">T3: WRAP</div>\n                    <i class=\"fa-solid fa-box-archive text-3xl text-slate-500 group-hover:text-emerald-400 mb-3 transition-colors text-shadow\"></i>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-300 text-xs mb-2\">AST PACKAGER</h3>\n                    <ul class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-mono list-disc pl-4 space-y-1\">\n                        <li>Compile to AST</li>\n                        <li>Generate Unit Tests</li>\n                        <li>Forward to Guardrail</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center\">The Assembly layer employs multiple micro-agents operating in a bounded team. It does not just generate a block of python; it builds the environment, maps the foreign schemas, writes the transformation logic, prepares unit tests for the VM, and outputs a functional AST block.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c6": {
        "title": "6. Guardrail Envelope",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nHardware-level sandboxing of unproven, AI-generated logic.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Firecracker microVM setup\n> 2) memory_limit=512MB, timeout=5s\n> 3) Mutates restricted to dummy DBs",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-[#00a2ed] border-b border-[#00a2ed]/50 pb-2\">6. ISOLATION GUARDRAIL</h2>\n            <div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center w-full max-w-3xl\">\n                <!-- The Sandbox -->\n                <div class=\"border-2 border-dashed border-[#00a2ed] rounded-3xl p-10 w-[600px] h-[300px] flex items-center justify-center relative bg-[#00a2ed]/5 shadow-[inset_0_0_50px_rgba(0,162,237,0.1)]\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute top-4 left-6 text-[#00a2ed] font-bold tracking-widest text-[10px]\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-shield-cat mr-2\"></i>FIRECRACKER MICRO-VM</div>\n                    <div class=\"absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-slate-500 font-mono text-[9px]\">RAM: 512MB | TIME: 5000ms</div>\n                    \n                    <!-- The Code inside -->\n                    <div class=\"bg-black border border-slate-800 rounded p-6 shadow-2xl flex items-center gap-6 relative z-10\">\n                        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-amber-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-500/50\">\n                            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-code text-amber-500 text-xl\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm leading-none mb-1\">Untrusted AST Logic</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-slate-500 font-mono text-[10px]\">Generated by Codegen Node C5</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <!-- Defensive walls -->\n                    <div class=\"absolute -left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-8 h-24 bg-rose-500/20 border-r border-rose-500/50 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-ban text-rose-500 text-xs\"></i></div>\n                    <div class=\"absolute -right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-8 h-24 bg-rose-500/20 border-l border-rose-500/50 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-ban text-rose-500 text-xs\"></i></div>\n                    <div class=\"absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-8 bg-[#00a2ed]/20 border-b border-[#00a2ed] flex items-center justify-center text-[#00a2ed] text-[8px] font-bold tracking-widest\">STRICT SECCOMP BPF</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center mt-4\">Before any generated code is permitted to execute or be validated, it is encapsulated within an isolated microVM. Network egress is blocked, file system access is denied, and strict computational limits prevent infinite loops or malicious behavior.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c10": {
        "title": "10. HITL Intervention",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nHuman oversight checkpoint for newly synthesized code structures.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) Halts process execution loop\n> 2) Displays diff to operations admin\n> 3) Wait-state until Authorize/Abort",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-yellow-500 border-b border-yellow-900 pb-2\">10. HUMAN IN THE LOOP (H.I.T.L)</h2>\n            <div class=\"bg-[#0a0701] border border-yellow-900/50 p-6 rounded shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(234,179,8,0.05)] w-full max-w-4xl\">\n                <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-yellow-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"text-white font-bold tracking-widest\">AUTHORIZATION REQUIRED</h3>\n                            <p class=\"text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase\">System paused at Node C10</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-right\">\n                        <div class=\"text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-mono\">Tier: HEAVY</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-mono mt-1\">Timeout in: <span class=\"text-yellow-500\">47:59:12</span></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-black/50 border border-rose-900/30 rounded p-4\">\n                        <div class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mb-2 border-b border-rose-900/30 pb-1\">Previous State</div>\n                        <pre class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-rose-300 opacity-60\">- function sync_db() {\n-   return false;\n- }</pre>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-black/50 border border-emerald-900/30 rounded p-4\">\n                        <div class=\"text-[9px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mb-2 border-b border-emerald-900/30 pb-1\">Generated State (AST)</div>\n                        <pre class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-300 opacity-80\">+ function sync_db(payload) {\n+   await databricks.insert(payload);\n+   return true;\n+ }</pre>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"flex gap-4 justify-center\">\n                    <button onclick=\"resolveHITL(false); closeDrilldown()\" class=\"bg-rose-900/20 hover:bg-rose-900/40 border border-rose-500 text-rose-400 px-8 py-2 rounded text-xs font-bold tracking-widest outline-none transition-colors\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-xmark mr-2\"></i> ABORT PIPELINE</button>\n                    <button onclick=\"resolveHITL(true); closeDrilldown()\" class=\"bg-emerald-900/20 hover:bg-emerald-900/40 border border-emerald-500 text-emerald-400 px-8 py-2 rounded text-xs font-bold tracking-widest outline-none transition-colors\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-check mr-2\"></i> AUTHORIZE PATCH</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center\">Heavy operations, such as generating novel GraphQL schemas or rolling back vulnerabilities, trigger a mandatory Human-In-The-Loop pause. The engine suspends its internal timers until an Architect physically approves the AST diff securely.</p>\n        </div>"
    },
    "c8": {
        "title": "8/9. Virtualize & Telemetry",
        "content": "**Procedural Goal**\nRun N-trials against dummy environments to prove deterministic reliability.\n\n**Deep Mechanics**\n> 1) SimulationAgent pushes dummy traffic\n> 2) StressTest verifies RAM/CPU load caps\n> 3) Telemetry pipes OTLP traces to Databricks",
        "htmlDrilldown": "<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 h-full space-y-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-[#00f2fe] border-b border-[#00f2fe]/50 pb-2\">8/9. VIRTUALIZATION & OTLP TELEMETRY</h2>\n            <div class=\"flex gap-8 w-full max-w-4xl justify-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-[#020b12] border border-[#00f2fe]/30 rounded p-4 shadow-lg\">\n                        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\">\n                            <span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-400\">TEST VECTORS</span>\n                            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-network-wired text-[#00f2fe]/50\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n                            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                                <div class=\"h-2 w-full bg-emerald-900/30 rounded overflow-hidden\">\n                                    <div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 w-full\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <span class=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-emerald-400\">1,402</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                                <div class=\"h-2 w-full bg-emerald-900/30 rounded overflow-hidden\">\n                                    <div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 w-[80%]\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <span class=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-emerald-400\">835</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                                <div class=\"h-2 w-full bg-rose-900/30 rounded overflow-hidden\">\n                                    <div class=\"h-full bg-rose-500 w-[5%]\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <span class=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-rose-400\">2</span>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700/50 p-3 rounded text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">\n                        > Spawn SimulationAgent<br>\n                        > Generate 2000 mock API contexts<br>\n                        > Pipe through Sandboxed AST<br>\n                        > Await deterministic stability\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center\">\n                    <div class=\"relative w-48 h-48 border-4 border-dashed border-[#00f2fe]/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite]\">\n                        <div class=\"absolute w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#00f2fe] top-0 shadow-[0_0_15px_#00f2fe]\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"absolute w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 bottom-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#3b82f6]\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"absolute flex flex-col items-center\">\n                        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-tower-broadcast text-3xl text-[#00f2fe] mb-2\"></i>\n                        <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-[#00f2fe] bg-black/50 px-2 rounded\">OPENTELEMETRY</span>\n                        <span class=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-slate-500 mt-1\">gRPC streaming to Datalake</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-mono tracking-wide max-w-2xl text-center mt-4\">Virtualization proves the mathematical validity of the AST by slamming it with thousands of synthetic test cases. Throughout this, Node 9 emits an infinite stream of OpenTelemetry performance tracing back 